4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge in the field. The course provides the necessary skills to start a career as a data scientist and build machine learning models. It is a 16-week program that covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also includes real-life case studies and emphasizes the use of industry-standard tools. Classes are taught in English or Spanish, and the class size is limited to a maximum of 12 people. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. More information can be found on their website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop